{"title":"俳句三首  送鉴真大师像返奈良并呈森本长老","authors":["赵朴初"],"dates":[{"year":1980,"month":5,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"俳句三首"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送鉴真大师像返奈良并呈森本长老"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赵朴初"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看尽杜鹃花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不因隔海怨天涯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东西都是家。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去住夏云闲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"招提灯共大明龛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双照泪痕乾。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万绿正参天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好凭风月结来缘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象教住人间。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九八○年五月二十八日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于首都机场"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}